{"tid":2195238,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"催淚氣增染武肺風險  國際人權報告促禁用","createTime":"2020-09-09T04:51:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T05:07:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5b566759916e40e545a77036da46398254849480","tid":2195238,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T04:51:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200909/PT32OQUEERE4RCWGNTIHXHAZNQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200909%2FPT32OQUEERE4RCWGNTIHXHAZNQ%2F&d=Yvf7L03l0%2FKFASkGPCPwg70p1Vm5vkyQgjvFoLOApLI%3D&h=b78b9420\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200909%2FPT32OQUEERE4RCWGNTIHXHAZNQ%2F&h=31a4bc66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200909/PT32OQUEERE4RCWGNTIHXHAZNQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n催淚氣增染武肺風險 <br />\n國際人權報告促禁用<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/IV0JwysnBI-qEoVKUEsDd56Pac4=/1979x1319/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CSY2ASJHORFQXCECQCOOD4Z6AM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FIV0JwysnBI-qEoVKUEsDd56Pac4%3D%2F1979x1319%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCSY2ASJHORFQXCECQCOOD4Z6AM.jpg&h=458dbb8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■今年5月警方在銅鑼灣及灣仔一帶放催淚彈，有市民將傷者抱離現場。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警方在反送中運動間狂轟逾1.6萬枚催淚彈，引起世界對濫用催淚彈的關注。有人權報告引述研究指出，接觸催淚氣體後一周感染呼吸疾病風險增加，逾千名美國衞生人員更憂慮會造成武漢肺炎傳染，聯署要求政府停止向示威者使用催淚氣體。報告又批評催淚氣體成為執法部門打壓和平集會的武器，其中香港和美國均有很多例子，要求透過國際人權法禁用。<br />\n<br />\n多倫多大學法學院國際人權項目日前發表報告，形容催淚氣體是危險和無差別的化學物體，並被各地執法部門濫用和武器化，打壓表達和集會自由。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n報告指出，誤用可導致健康風險，當警方向人直射催淚彈，可造成頭部創傷、瘀傷和骨折，在伊拉克有直射頭部致死個案，長期或大量接觸催淚氣體可引致失明、喉嚨和肺部化學灼傷、呼吸衰竭，引致死亡，有呼吸道或心臟問題的人士亦會增加呼吸驟停或心臟病發風險。<br />\n<br />\n報告特別提及香港曾在密閉空間施放催淚，令風險增加。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ssm1wCNDT0EUdwfHpSTXkOTCOts=/662x566/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UC766KQDRRB4NC7JLBSSOQEPMA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fssm1wCNDT0EUdwfHpSTXkOTCOts%3D%2F662x566%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUC766KQDRRB4NC7JLBSSOQEPMA.jpg&h=0e959ecb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n指銷售無監管毒性不明<br />\n<br />\n一項2014年研究發現，美軍士兵接觸催淚氣體後一周，較易感染呼吸系統疾病。報告認為，吸入氣體的人士會激烈咳嗽，在武漢肺炎大流行下，增加播毒機會。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n報告認為，催淚氣體銷售和貿易很大程度上不受監管，催淚彈成份及其毒性不明，有需要對不同催淚彈效果做更多研究。<br />\n<br />\n報告又指出，催淚彈已在戰場上禁用，其無差異性不能做到合符武力比例，尤其會被用作侵害人權和向兒童和長者等弱勢群體使用。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n香港人權監察發言人葉寬柔表示，去年香港連串示威後，引起國際對催淚彈誤用的關注，。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n警方回應稱過去使用催淚煙等武力均源自有非法集結、違法堵路和暴力襲擊他人等，以催淚煙製造安全距離，避免出現近距離衝突，又否認曾在密封地方使用催淚煙。"},{"pid":"19771e8bf0ff15783e7d6b5696d6c2d379780c93","tid":2195238,"uid":11291,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T04:53:32.000Z","msg":"留名等睇禁左之後黑警照放催淚彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37451286e817f34b2eff756ddeb55191c2d648a0","tid":2195238,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T04:59:54.000Z","msg":"黑警仲惡過大陸公安<br />\n仲點會聽你講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3d5e9ad53b1cf0d25af89b3524fad74677836f1","tid":2195238,"uid":301479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T05:03:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"489579e6ad644bc5b4fded794c6cffd3a459a217","tid":2195238,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T05:07:09.000Z","msg":"推推先"}]}